Interface com.chimu.form.mapping.CollectiveObjectRetriever

public interface CollectiveObjectRetriever
extends ObjectRetriever
A CollectiveObjectRetriever supports retrieval of heterogeneous objects that are all mapped using a DistinguishingObjectMapper.
